Business Brief -- Stanley Works:
   Two Units of AXIA Inc.,
   Tool Concerns, Are Bought
Goldblatt Tool Co., which makes masonry, tile and drywall
tools, employs 180 people at facilities in Kansas and
California. Mail Media markets Jensen Tools through catalog
sales for electronic technicians, communication service
personnel and precision mechanics. Jensen employs 200 people
in Arizona and Delaware.
   Stanley Works in 1991 had sales of almost $2 billion.